        <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Hd1e108">Rubrica 37</head>
        <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De confessione et indulgentia peccatorum</head>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e114">
          De confessione et indul<lb ed="#B"/>gencia
          peccatorum Rubrica 37
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e121">
          <lb ed="#B"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e118">PSalmista 31</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e125">Beati
          quorum sunt iniquitates
          et quorum tecta etcetera</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e135">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e132">Idem C17</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e137">Confitemini
          domino etcetera
          </quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e144">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e145">Salomon in prouerbiorum capitulo 28</ref>
          <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e148">Qui abscondit scelera sua non dirigetur
          qui autem confessus fuerit et reliquerit
          ea misericordiam consequetur</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e162">
          [omitted]
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e170">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e175">Yesus filius
          sydrach in ecclesiastico capitulo 4</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e174">Non confundar confiteri 
          peccata tua</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e180">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e185">Idem capitulo XI</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e182">Viuus et
          sanus confiteberis et laudabis deum
          et glorificaberis in miserationibus illius</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e188">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e197">Mattheus VI</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e192">Si dimiseritis hominibus peccata 
          eorum etcetera</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e202">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e213">Marcus XI</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e206">Cum stabitis
          ad orandum dimittite siquid habetis
          aduersus aliquem</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e215">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e228">Lucas VI</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e219">Dimittite 
          et dimittetur uobis</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e225">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e238">Idem XVII</ref>
          <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e227">Si peccauerit in te fratur tuus etcetera</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e239">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e256">Ioannes prima
          capitulo I</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e243">Si confiteamur peccatam nostra fidelis et
          iustus est dominus ut dimittat peccata 
          nostra nobis et emundet nos ab omni iniquitate</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e251">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e270">Iacobus V et finale</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e255">Confiteamini
          alterutrum peccata uestra</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e261">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e282">Paulus romanus X</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e265">Cor<pb ed="#C" n="14-v"/><cb ed="#C" n="a"/>de 
          autem creditur ad iustitiam ore autem confessio 
          fit ad salutem
          </quote>
        </p>
        <p>
          ¶ Boetius libro primo
          capitulo VIIIo Si operam medicantis exspectes
          opertet ut uulnus deteges
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e271">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e294">ysidorus
          in sinonima soliloquiorum libro I capitulo XIIo</ref>
          <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e275">Confessio sanat confessio iustificat confessio 
          peccatis veniam donat nulla tam
          grauis est culpa quod non habeat veniam</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e286">
          ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Rd1e309">Idem XVI et finale</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e288">Frequenter peccatis
          et lugens uix veniam meretur</quote>
        </p>
      </div>
